1. login to linux machine
   (environment setting in "source.me.first" is for linux OS)
2. use tcsh (/bin/tcsh) or csh (/bin/csh) 

3. source source.me.first

4 Schematic/Layout : Cadence Virtuoso
	1. go to Cadence directory
	2. virtuoso&

5 Hspice simulation
	1. go to Hspice directory
	2. run or run.monte
	3. wv& (view simulation waveform)

*. Directory structure
	: Cadence - virtuoso directory
	: Hspice - hspice simulation directory
	: FreePDK45 - 45nm free design kit directory
